{"tid":1417370,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"港共陰謀劇本推演","createTime":"2019-08-05T16:27:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T16:17:05.000Z","uid":232748,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9b90a3752143aa21ac16c66f95c25319d6ac43fb","tid":1417370,"uid":232748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:27:32.000Z","msg":"今日一路發夢，一路睇住實況<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n由性騷擾個女示威者，到今日777既講話<br />\n<br />\n不禁令人聯想:<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">港共是否演緊一個劇本，將示威者黑警化？</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黑警兇市民vs示威者罵市民影相<br />\n<br />\n黑警亂開槍vs示威者誤攻紀錄部隊宿舍<br />\n<br />\n黑警打記者vs示威者拆cctvb車<br />\n<br />\n黑警濫武vs示威者放火狗屋燒狗車</span></span><br />\n<br />\n如果示威者有埋黑社會<br />\n就完美演繹777口中暴徒角色....<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外今日<br />\n<br />\n我地由不合作開始，到7區激戰<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地完全無俾大罷工去發酵</span></span><br />\n<br />\n7區塞爆人的大罷工，係香港係一個壯舉<br />\n<br />\n但今日係大眾眼中會係乜？<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">傳媒只會放大暴力行為</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n而777講到明日日記者會<br />\n各位，民意戰開打了？<br />\n<br />\n各位仲記得我地當初的先文後武嘛<br />\n<br />\n能打出自己的組合就是屬於自己的節奏。能夠打出多變的組合，就是一個好拳手<br />\n<br />\n兄弟，唔好比人被挑釁，唔好比人帶節奏了<br />\n<br />\n如果做革命無民意<br />\n同做人無公關一樣<br />\n咪食撚屎囉"},{"pid":"553e5a36c5972fa942e2e8105c25377ec0f8c373","tid":1417370,"uid":280349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:28:04.000Z","msg":"再post: 文宣攻勢開始啦，打左啲野大家幫手spread啊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1417298\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1417298</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7f89d0b3e06286dfec9668b37249bd658203aeaa","tid":1417370,"uid":222190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:30:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7Ft2dx6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx